  "body": "#### Summary:\r\nPerforming KZG checks after DB writes in regular sync exposes a DOS risk. The proposer must be willing sacrifice the block to exploit it.\r\n\r\n#### Proposed Solution:\r\n- Save blobs to cache first.\r\n- Perform KZG checks on cached blobs.\r\n- Move blobs to DB only after passing checks.",
